---
const url = Astro.url.pathname;
const isEnglish = url.includes('/en/');
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="blog-footer">
  {isEnglish ? (
    <>
      <p>© {currentYear} Dayul · <a href="https://lukyday-blog.vercel.app">lukyday-blog.vercel.app</a></p>
      <p>Knowledge sharing is always welcome! However, please ensure to credit the source when sharing this post. Commercial use or unauthorized reproduction is prohibited.</p>
      <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://licensebuttons.net/l/by-nc-nd/4.0/88x31.png" alt="CC BY-NC-ND 4.0" />
      </a>
      <p>Owl icon by <a href="https://www.flaticon.com" target="_blank">Flaticon</a></p>
    </>
  ) : (
    <>
      <p>© {currentYear} Dayul · <a href="https://lukyday-blog.vercel.app">lukyday-blog.vercel.app</a></p>
      <p>지식 공유를 환영합니다! 다만, 본 포스팅의 내용을 공유하실 때는 반드시 출처를 밝혀주시기 바랍니다. 영리적 목적의 무단 전재 및 재배포는 금지하고 있습니다.</p>
      <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://licensebuttons.net/l/by-nc-nd/4.0/88x31.png" alt="CC BY-NC-ND 4.0" />
      </a>
      <p>Owl icon by <a href="https://www.flaticon.com" target="_blank">Flaticon</a></p>
    </>
  )}
</footer>

<style>
  .blog-footer {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
  }
  .blog-footer a {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .blog-footer img {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .blog-footer img:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>